    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that remains in absolute showroom condition. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment and has never been exposed to inclement weather. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free from any stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium upholstery shows no creasing, the carpets are spotless, and it has never been smoked in. Every feature, from the sophisticated infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified specialists\u2014full documentation is included. The engine bay is detailed and pristine, reflecting the care this vehicle has received. This is a rare chance to acquire a turn-key, investment-grade automobile that drives exactly as it did the day it was delivered. Sold with all original manuals, two sets of keys, and a bespoke car cover.",
